<bibRefCitation id="E13C4B75DA47FFA143C3FA5DEDB8F983" author="MCCOY T. A. &amp; LAVRANOS J. J." box="[677,975,1515,1541]" pageId="5" pageNumber="18" pagination="126 - 128" refId="ref4588" refString="MCCOY T. A. &amp; LAVRANOS J. J. 2007. - A coastal and a montane new species of Madagascan Aloe. Cactus and Succulent Journal 79 (3): 126 - 128." type="journal article" year="2007">McCoy &amp; Lavranos (2007)</bibRefCitation>
